@model Redfern.Web.Models.ResetPasswordEmail
To: @Model.To
Subject: Redfern Password Reset Confirmation

Hi @Model.UserFullName,

This email was automatically sent by Redfern in response to your request to reset your password.  

To reset your password and access your account, click on the link below:

@Html.Raw(Model.ResetLink).  

If clicking the link did not work, try copying and pasting it into the address bar of your browser.

If you did not request to reset your password, please disregard this message.  This link will expire within 72 hours.

Thanks,
The Redfern Team
